editorialNotes.standard: Bookend your days with a moment of reflection in stoic., an elegantly designed journaling app made for anyone looking to carve out time for mindfulness. editorialNotes.standard: If you’re like us, you need all the help you can get turning rare quiet moments into true meditation. Oh, and we love how Headspace’s Apple Watch app lets you hit a literal panic button when extra-stressful situations arise.

editorialNotes.standard: Take a deep breath: it’s both a call to action and a defining feature of this app’s approach to meditation. In a crowded field of mindfulness apps, it stands out for its ease of use and attention to (soothing) detail.
